[INAUDIBLE]

00:43:37.597 --> 00:43:39.722
MATT BRITTIN: Let's take
a photograph before we go.

00:43:39.722 --> 00:43:40.706
A photograph for everybody.

00:43:40.706 --> 00:43:41.198
Not me.

00:43:41.198 --> 00:43:42.198
RIO FERDINAND: With you.

00:43:42.198 --> 00:43:44.150
MATT BRITTIN: Just you.

00:43:44.150 --> 00:43:46.303
RIO FERDINAND:
Thank you, cheers.

